### What is {COIN} Staking?
{COIN} Staking is an on-chain staking product of Gate.io, which allows users to stake {COIN} and delegate it to validators on {Network} through Gate.io. Users can also easily earn on-chain rewards.
### {COIN} Staking Rules
If you stake {COIN} on a given calendar day (00:00 - 23:59 UTC), you will receive {REWARD} at a 1:{ExchangeRate} ratio and earn daily {REWARD} rewards.
Minimum staking amount:{MortgageMin} {COIN}
Staking limit: {MortgageLimt} 
Daily max staking amount: {MortgageMax} 
### {COIN} Redemption Rules
As a {REWARD} holder, you can redeem your {REWARD} back to {COIN} at a {ExchangeRate}:1 ratio. Your principal and return will be credited to your account immediately after submitting a redemption request.
Minimum redemption amount:{RedeemMin} {COIN}
Daily max redemption amount: {RedeemMax} 
### What is {REWARD}?
{REWARD} is a reward-generating liquid staking token and the representation of your staked {COIN} at a 1:{ExchangeRate} ratio.

